data.description: ***Now offering $5000 towards buyer's closing costs***  Come and see this beautiful single level, 4 bedroom home in the popular Mesquite Trails subdivision of East El Paso.  Entertaining both inside and out will be a breeze with the open concept floor plan and a backyard covered patio complete with fireplace and built in grill. You'll love having two living areas, a kitchen with granite counter tops, stainless appliances and an area for bar stools plus a zoned primary bedroom with a custom built walk in closet and a master bath with double vanity, separate shower and a relaxing garden tub.  The roof shingles were replaced in July 2023! Both the front and back yards are landscaped.  A two car garage and parking on the side is icing on the cake.  There is so much to love about this great home and it is easy to see so call for your appointment today!
